### TOOLS ###

## thyme - pomodoro timer
# https://github.com/hughbien/thyme
# bind keys to start/stop pom timer
bind-key P run "thyme -d"\; display-message "pomodoro!"
bind-key S run "thyme -s"\; display-message "done with pomodoro"


